cards.title: Sea Tower Tel Aviv
cards.subtitle: Hotel
cards.description: A magnificent beacon that graces the Mediterranean shoreline, the Sea Tower Tel Aviv is an urban delight perfectly situated at the heart of the non-stop city's business, tourism, and commercial districts. There's simply no better option for business travelers seeking to relax after a busy workday, in a friendly, welcoming atmosphere.

cards.title: Josef flowers boutique
cards.subtitle: Flowers
cards.description: Flower boutique for people who love! Explosive creativity, true passion for flowers and design, service always with a smile, deliveries to the entire region. With us you will enjoy a crazy selection of flower bouquets, arrangements, bridal bouquets, car decorations, balloons, flowers for the mother, event design, deliveries and all in one phone call!

cards.title: Gordon-pool
cards.subtitle: pool
cards.description: The famous Gordon Pool was established in 1956, and soon became a hub of social activity and one of the most renowned symbols of early Tel Aviv. Since its foundation, the Gordon Pool has been a municipal center belonging to the Tel Aviv-Jaffa Municipality’s Culture and Sports Division.
